                            <comment id="393527" author="pjones" created="Sat, 18 Nov 2023 22:03:34 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Landed for 2.16&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="393501" author="gerrit" created="Sat, 18 Nov 2023 21:43:20 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&quot;Oleg Drokin &amp;lt;green@whamcloud.com&amp;gt;&quot; merged in patch &lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/c/fs/lustre-release/+/52973/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/c/fs/lustre-release/+/52973/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
Subject: &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-17156&quot; title=&quot;sanityn test_16j: timeout&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-17156&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-17156&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; tests: Improve zfs_or_rotational()&lt;br/&gt;
